author: Google
description:
Don't just talk about your movie idea. Show it. 🎬

Hear from https://www.youtube.com/@metapuppet  on how Flow can help you prototype ideas, letting you move from concept to execution faster.

"If you're a filmmaker... you have to start playing around with it... Don't just talk about it, create it and then show them.”

Over the coming weeks, we're sharing unique workflows and tips from more creators pushing their boundaries. Make sure to follow so you don't miss the next episode!

Try Flow for yourself: https://flow.google
